summary: CONSUMER'S VEHICLE WAS HIT ON THE LEFT FRONT SIDE WITH AT AN ANGLE BY ANOTHER ANOTHER CAR TRAVELING APPROXIMATELY 40-.  THE DRIVER'S AIR BAG DEPLOYED, BUT THE PASSENGER AIR BAG DID NOT.  CONSUMER VERY CONCERNED BECAUSE COLLISION CAUSED EXTENSIVE DAMAGE TO VEHICLE INCLUDING A BENT FRAME.  CONSUMER FEELS THE SEVERITY OF THE COLLISION SHOULD HAVE CAUSED THE PASSENGER SIDE BAG TO DEPLOY.
